  "titles": "World Eaters Red Hand Destroyer Assault Squad",
  "lore": "Many Red Hand squads sought to requisition jump packs to aid them in closing with their foe as swiftly as possible. Crashing down from above, they often crushed opponents beneath their ceramite sabatons. Attacking with an insatiable fury, their hacking blades slick with blood and gun barrels glowing white-hot, they roved the fields of battle seeking ever more lives to bring to an end, leaving the ground slick with blood. Pausing only to clear the motors of their chainblades of gory residue, they would wordlessly trigger their jump packs again and soar away in search of fresh victims to slake their wrath upon.",
